title: Ben Leber and Nordo Friday FEAST!
description: It's a Friday Football Feast sans PA and Charch, but don't worry, Ben Leber and Nordo have you covered! Mike Florio joins only because Ben played for the Vikings, plus Leber and Reggie Bush go down memory lane recalling the 2009 NFC Champ.
